<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The index.php generated by Zend_Tool (trunk revision 15149) generates the following code:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$application-&gt;bootstrap()
            -&gt;run();
</code></pre>

<p>Unfortunately, Zend_Application::bootstrap() is defined as:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function bootstrap()
{
    $this-&gt;getBootstrap()-&gt;bootstrap();
}
</code></pre>

<p>Either Zend_Application::bootstrap() should {{return $this;}} or Zend_Tool should generate code like this:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$application-&gt;bootstrap()
$application-&gt;run();
</code></pre>

    </div>
</div>

